high_descs: Turn left and go as far as the dishwasher then turn left and go as far as the table and turn left to face the table
Pick up the knife from the table
Turn left and go straight to the counter then turn right and then left to face the sink
Put the knife in the sink and turn on the water, then turn off the water and get the knife from the sink
Turn left and go to the edge of the counter on the left
Put the knife in the drawer second from the bottom, next to the dishwasher
anns.task_desc: Put a washed knife in a drawer

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the counter and walk to the black counter on the left.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the right side of the black counter.
Turn left, hang a right at the counter and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the knife inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn left to face the drawers to the left of the dishwasher.
Put the rinsed knife inside the third drawer down from the top and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed knife in a drawer.

high_descs: pick up the knife from the table
rinse the knife with water and take it out
move left to the drawer under the oven
place the knife in the drawer
anns.task_desc: place a clean knife in a drawer under the table
